&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Using an RF scanner, identify and pull items to build customer orders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Frequently move boxes weighing up to 60 pounds throughout the fulfillment center&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operate a hand truck, pallet jack, or electric pallet jack to move inventory across the fulfillment center&lt;/li&gt;
